Backend specific definition of amp condition variable to allow placing a condition variable on the stack. Platform specific headers will be included.

Attention:
Don't copy a variable of type amp_raw_condition_variable_s - copying a pointer to this type is ok though.

Function Documentation

int amp_raw_condition_variable_finalize ( amp_condition_variable_t  cond  ) 

Like amp_condition_variable_destroy but does not free memory for the amp condition variable other than indirectly via the platform API to destroy a platform condition variable.

int amp_raw_condition_variable_init ( amp_condition_variable_t  cond  ) 

Like amp_condition_variable_create but does not allocate memory for the amp conditon variable other than indirectly via the platform API to create a platform condition variable.
